      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Let us see whether Elias will come.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "—Here again we have eager expectation rather than derision. Was the “great and dreadful day” (",
        "children": []
