      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Malachi 4:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") about to burst on them? Would the long-expected prophet at last appear? The sponge and vinegar would seem to minds thus on the stretch an unworthy interruption of the catastrophe of the great drama of which they were spectators.",
